          Platform Engineering
        :kramdown
          We started with  stability, improving #{define("test coverage")} and performance for the thousands of people already relying on the service. With the site experiencing prolonged periods of high traffic, we were able to improve uptime and make a lot of the data processing done behind the scenes more efficient.

          Next, it was on to implementing user-requested features like private messaging and premium subscriptions. We wrote a system to handle payment transactions, allowing HSMers to pay a small amount monthly and unlock extra features.
