          Social Strategy
        :kramdown
          Working on a platform with such a thriving community is a challenge and a privilege. We're always looking to the future with the HSM team, advising them on how best to satisfy users and the technical feasibility of requested features.

          We utilise [Mixpanel](https://mixpanel.com/) to give HSM a valuable insight into user activity. Data collected throughout the site helps guide changes to the interface and flags up popular user-generated content for the HSM staff to feature.

          With lots of ideas for the website and plans for Terracoding to bring HSM to the iPhone, we're excited to continue helping the community to grow and make a difference.
